      <title>移动网络市场在长期衰退后看到“一线希望”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/mobile-networks-market-sees-glimmer-of-hope-after-long-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Dell’Oro Group Inc. 的一份报告显示，多年来无线接入网络需求下滑已导致移动设备制造商爱立信和诺基亚的销售受到重创，但这一趋势正在显现稳定迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/mobile-networks-market-sees-glimmer-of-hope-after-long-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 14:13:05 GMT</pubDate>
